snippet.textDisplay: wow Sajjad Ali wow! he has always been enthralling and superb with his soft, soul-touching voice and Farheen's vocals are superbly complimenting Sajjad's soft voice. Kudos to COKE STUDIO PAKISTAN for producing such captivating, and phenomenal content one after another. This season will definitely be remembered for a long, long time.
